---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Terms & Conditions" description="Reservation, cancellation, and shipping terms for Vechornytsi dinners and shop orders.">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 md:pt-24 pb-8">
    <div class="max-w-[52rem]">
      <span class="kicker">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.05] mt-4">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="container-reading flex flex-col gap-5 text-ink leading-relaxed">
      <p><span class="font-medium">Reservations.</span> A seat is confirmed once payment clears. Reservations open 14 days before each dinner and are limited to twelve seats. Dinner tickets are non-refundable but transferable — send us the name of your replacement.</p>
      <p><span class="font-medium">Allergies.</span> The menu changes weekly with the forage. Note allergies when you book and we will accommodate them with advance notice.</p>
      <p><span class="font-medium">Gift vouchers.</span> Redeemable for one seat at any upcoming dinner, valid six months from purchase, non-refundable, transferable.</p>
      <p><span class="font-medium">Shipping.</span> Pantry goods and ceramics ship within Ukraine. Gift vouchers are delivered digitally and can be bought from anywhere.</p>
      <p>Questions? Write to <a href="mailto:tanyazavodenko188@gmail.com" class="text-accent">tanyazavodenko188@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
